{"tid":15710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉小麗如被取消資格　非建制分組否權危在旦夕","createTime":"2016-12-01T06:06:12.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-01T07:57:55.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f3adc5fa4a1bbb0bdd0af5320d66542b34dc853","tid":15710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:06:12.000Z","msg":"隨着梁頌恆、游蕙禎被取消資格，一旦政府成功覆核劉小麗宣誓，令她失去議員資格，在補選前「空窗期」，<strong>非建制派在立法會地區直選組別由原本的19席，減至16席，與建制派議席數目一樣，分組否決權危在旦夕。</strong><br />\n<br />\n按議事規則，由議員提出的議案、修改議事規則等，需要同時獲得功能組別和地區直選兩分組，在席的過半數議員支持方可通過，意味只要有一名地區直選的非建制議員不在席，建制派或可成功偷襲。"},{"pid":"3ec588116762b46f4a8a67af86ea943d40f25c4c","tid":15710,"uid":6041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"一早就話唇亡齒寒架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c5a4e0ddbad3852afe55122e5c43aebb53a0679","tid":15710,"uid":42350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:09:13.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"56b5e2ee028a2f380cdaedb594adb346ba5b1934","tid":15710,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:27:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11d678781136ff7fec677b57c424e6949627fe14","tid":15710,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:28:17.000Z","msg":"屌 佢玩撚哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f10bb07677b7fbea3a567098c83ed1a0f46023c","tid":15710,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-01T06:29:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬： who fuckin care<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有一隻係你樓上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif